PROBLEM   NUMBER                                            :                                             3370. Smallest Number With All Set Bits

//  Wednesday, 29 October 2025


// Bit Manipulation

/*
 | Concept            | Description                                         |
| ------------------ | --------------------------------------------------- |
| **Goal**           | Find smallest number ≥ `n` that has all bits = 1    |
| **Formula**        | `x = 2^k - 1`                                       |
| **Loop logic**     | Keep doubling `x` and adding 1 until it exceeds `n` |
| **Binary pattern** | 1 → 11 → 111 → 1111 → ...                           |

*/
class Solution {
public:
    int smallestNumber(int n) {
        int x = 1;
        while (x < n) {
            x = x * 2 + 1;
        }
        return x;
    }
};
